# Matcha Hotel UI Rules

This project uses TypeUI **Matcha** for all UI. Follow these rules on every change.

## Required skills (read before UI work)

1. `.agents/skills/typeui-fundamentals/` — accessibility, spacing, typography, UX guardrails
2. `.agents/skills/typeui-design-system/SKILL.md` — Matcha tokens and components
3. `.agents/skills/serene-stays-hotel/SKILL.md` — page structure and content tone

## Design tokens (never override with random values)

- Surface `#F6F2E8`, Section `#DBF2D0`, Brand `#314535`, Brand Medium `#AEC2A4`
- Heading `#2B3A2E`, Body `#4A5547`
- Fonts: Noto Serif (headings), Noto Sans (body)
- Radius: 4px. Spacing: 8px grid. Min touch target: 48px.

## Architecture

- Primitives → `src/components/ui/`
- Sections → `src/components/sections/`
- Content/data → `src/lib/content.ts`
- `page.tsx` composes sections only

## Do not

- Use Geist fonts, pill buttons, gold accents, or dark mode
- Add unrelated dependencies without need
- Weaken accessibility for aesthetics
